Rules.InvariantScript: If(IsBlank(compSearch.IconSearchOpenNewX), If(App.Width < 500, searchBox_1.Width - Self.Width * 2, searchBox_1.Width - Self.Width * 2.5), compSearch.IconSearchOpenNewX)
If(IsBlank(compSearch.NewHintText), If(searchBox_1.Width < 450, "Search", "Search by ticket id, title, or description"), compSearch.NewHintText)
If(searchIcon_1.Visible, searchBox_1.X + searchBox_1.Width - searchIcon_1.Width - Self.Width, searchBox_1.X + searchBox_1.Width - Self.Width)

CustomProperties.Name: NewHintText
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Sets the new hint text for search bar

CustomProperties.Name: SearchVisible
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Determines if search bar is visible in mobile view

CustomProperties.Name: IconSearchOpenNewX
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Sets a new x position for the open search icon

CustomProperties.Name: OpenSearch
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Makes search bar visible in mobile view

CustomProperties.Name: CloseSearch
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Makes search bar not visible in mobile view

CustomProperties.Name: GetIconSearchOpenWidth
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Returns the width of the search open icon
